You were probably flustered because it was more then you expected.

616
00:47:22,024 --> 00:47:25,171
How could you make such serious misunderstanding?

617
00:47:28,370 --> 00:47:31,230
Your taste is very...

618
00:47:31,661 --> 00:47:33,171
Hello?

619
00:47:33,396 --> 00:47:35,031
Unni!

620
00:47:35,031 --> 00:47:39,149
Can you whisper it to me this time?

621
00:47:39,665 --> 00:47:41,605
You want me to press 060 for you?

622
00:47:42,993 --> 00:47:45,431
<i>Hello?</i>

623
00:47:45,694 --> 00:47:49,088
<i>Is there anyone there?</i>

624
00:47:50,612 --> 00:47:53,387
<i>The darkness,</i>

625
00:47:53,387 --> 00:47:57,433
<i>has already overspread into the night.</i>

626
00:47:58,636 --> 00:48:02,315
<i>Knocking on the window and answering to the moonlight.</i>

627
00:48:41,606 --> 00:48:43,833
He’s not good news.

628
00:48:44,402 --> 00:48:47,077
It's probably your company's motto.

629
00:48:48,491 --> 00:48:52,212
I’m telling you to be careful,
