as I want as long as I’m next to you.

632
00:49:33,186 --> 00:49:34,531
Go in.

633
00:50:06,761 --> 00:50:08,490
What are you doing?

634
00:50:08,490 --> 00:50:11,157
Oh, you came?

635
00:50:13,333 --> 00:50:16,643
Why did you ride the taxi by yourself? It’s dangerous.

636
00:50:17,012 --> 00:50:20,530
Why should I go on the road that you drop off Ji Sun?

637
00:50:20,813 --> 00:50:23,337
So what?

638
00:50:25,872 --> 00:50:27,949
I’m coming home anyways.

639
00:50:27,949 --> 00:50:30,823
Please, play by yourselves.

640
00:50:31,304 --> 00:50:33,729
Ji Sun’s taking care of you because you catch her eye.

641
00:50:33,729 --> 00:50:38,455
I know. And that’s why I went along up till now.

642
00:50:38,668 --> 00:50:40,213
But don’t do it anymore.

643
00:50:40,497 --> 00:50:42,484
It’s tiring.

644
00:50:58,578 --> 00:51:01,671
<i>Yes, I've returned home safely.</i>

645
00:51:28,687 --> 00:51:31,367
Hey, let’s go to the bath.

646
00:51:32,203 --> 00:51:34,629
- Is it okay?
