649
00:51:41,517 --> 00:51:44,875
Go just the two of you to fish in the weekend.

650
00:51:45,881 --> 00:51:46,772
Why?

651
00:51:46,772 --> 00:51:52,238
She's very excited about going fishing with you only, idiot!

652
00:51:55,856 --> 00:51:57,948
Let’s change a bit.

653
00:52:01,600 --> 00:52:04,338
About me splitting me with Jun Mo.

654
00:52:05,122 --> 00:52:08,876
If it wasn’t back when I was 20 and it was now,

655
00:52:08,876 --> 00:52:12,652
