656
00:52:12,914 --> 00:52:14,263
You think so?

657
00:52:14,263 --> 00:52:15,815
Yeah.

658
00:52:16,604 --> 00:52:19,139
When I see my married friends,

659
00:52:19,481 --> 00:52:24,811
well, I don’t mind Sang Hoon and Mi Kyung
because they’re both our friends,

660
00:52:25,067 --> 00:52:29,452
