692
00:54:24,849 --> 00:54:27,625
I’m not to that extent.

693
00:54:32,562 --> 00:54:34,843
<i>Actually, my heart ached.</i>

694
00:54:35,074 --> 00:54:38,010
<i>I hated the girl that made me think like this,</i>

695
00:54:38,259 --> 00:54:43,493
