girl’s beside Hyung Tae, and not me,</i>

696
00:54:43,493 --> 00:54:46,778
<i>a 30 year old jealousy aroused.</i>

697
00:54:46,778 --> 00:54:57,431
<i>I was sad that what seemed like a heavy
30 years could fly away like ear hair.</i>

698
00:55:05,520 --> 00:55:09,761
