706
00:56:36,996 --> 00:56:38,065
Alright.

707
00:56:38,065 --> 00:56:39,908
Let’s do it.

708
00:56:54,485 --> 00:56:57,184
It’s actually ok to live apart.

709
00:56:57,404 --> 00:56:58,946
You become my alcohol buddy.

710
00:56:58,946 --> 00:57:01,504
Be quiet.

711
00:57:05,980 --> 00:57:07,552
Here.

712
00:57:11,244 --> 00:57:13,225
