714
00:57:15,943 --> 00:57:17,381
You ask such things.

715
00:57:17,381 --> 00:57:19,762
Just for the heck of it.

716
00:57:20,032 --> 00:57:24,421
Tell me honestly. When was the last time you loved?

717
00:57:24,421 --> 00:57:26,534
Just eat your food.

718
00:57:28,218 --> 00:57:30,038
When will you grow up?

719
00:57:30,038 --> 00:57:32,890
I don’t know what maturity is,

720
00:57:34,030 --> 00:57:35,773
