734
00:59:18,599 --> 00:59:20,325
Mom.

735
00:59:20,819 --> 00:59:23,824
Can you hug me once?

736
00:59:34,798 --> 00:59:36,944
Don’t be uncomfortable.

737
00:59:37,763 --> 00:59:40,509
